quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  16,111,"Inyanga yabuli omundu alitsa okhwikomelela omwene, ne buli omundu alirungwa amalayi kayakholanga"
  16,112,"Nyasaye abachelasilinjia olukongo lwali nende omulembe nende obwihotselefu, omukabo kukwe kwabetselanga mubunji, okhurula buli elubeka. Halali nikukhaya tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye, mana Nyasaye nakufwala eshifwalo shieyinzala nende oburi khulwokhubeela kalia akabakholanga"
  16,113,"Ne Omurumwa yabetsela okhurula mubo, mana nibamuyingasia, mana eshinyasio nishiboolela nibalibo abeene bekholela obubii"
  16,114,"Ne mulie khubilia bia Nyasaye abahelesiyie, ebiamwachamilwa ebilayi, ne mukhupe orio khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye, toto nimuli mbu mumulamanga"
  16,115,"Yabakania okhulia shifwile, nende amalasile, nende inyama yeyimbitsi, nende shisinzilwe nishilarumbulilwekho elira lia Nyasaye tawe, khu ulia unichililisibwa bilali okhuloba nohomba okhubura eshichelo tawe, awo toto Nyasaye ni omunji wobulesheli Owetsimbabaasi"
  16,116,"Ne mulaboola khububeyi bwetsinimi tsienyu mbu : “ shino shiafuchililwa ne shino shiakanibwa.” muletsa mwachishila Nyasaye obubeyi. Toto bachishilanga Nyasaye obubeyi shibalibura tawe"
  16,117,"omwikhoyo mutiti butwsa, nebalinyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo muno"
  16,118,"Ne Abayahudi khwabakania akakhubakaniile khale awo, ne shikhwabakholela obubii tawe, halali bo abeene nibekholela obubii"
  16,119,"Mana toto Nyasaye wuwo khubalia bakholanga obubii khubulamanya mana nibekanila nibakhakhola ako, mana nibakhola amalayi, toto Nyasaye wuwo imbeli wa ako ni Omunji wokhuleshela Omunji westimbabaasi"
  16,120,"Toto Ibrahim yali Omwimilisi, Omwihotselefu khu Nyasaye, Omutswenufu neshiyali Omutsokaasi tawe"
  16,121,Yali omukhupi wa orio khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye. Mana namwawula khunjila ingolofu
  16,122,"Mana nikhumuhelesia mushialo amalayi, naye mwikulu aliba mubandu abalayi"
  16,123,"Mana nikhukhufimbulila mbu : “oloonde emilukha chia Ibrahim owaria Nyasaye, ne shiyali mubatsokasi tawe.”"
  16,124,"Toto jumamosi yarebwaho khubalia bakabukhanamwo khuyo, ne toto Nyasaye alibabusilia inyanga yeyindukho khukalia akabakabukhanangamwo"
  16,125,"Langa khunjila ya Nyasaye wuwo mumachesi, nende amachelo amalayi, ne olomalome nabo munjila indayi, toto Nyasaye wuwo amanyile ulia uwakora injila yiyie ne amanyile muno balia abalunjikha"
  16,126,Ne nimurunga imoongo murunge ebihelana nende ebia mukholelwe amabii. Ne nimwifwila toto awo nobulayi khubalia abefwilanga
  16,127,"Ne wifwile, ne okhwifwila khwukhwo khulaba halali khulwa Nyasaye butswa, ne olabeelela shichila bo tawe, ne olaba mubunyakhani shichila kabatutanga tawe"
  16,128,"Toto Nyasaye ali halala nende balia bamuria, nende balia abakholanga amalayi"